About This Company
Reach Group was founded in 1999 in the Gulf Region, particularly in Abu Dhabi - U.A.E It operates in three main areas: Management Consulting, Information Technology, Recruitment & Outsourcing services.
Reach Group has three offices in U.A.E. (Abu Dhabi, Dubai and Sharjah) in addition to other two offices in Kuwait and Jordan. Reach Group's activities cover most Arab countries and several foreign countries through a network of Business Development experts who are permanently employed or outsourced by Reach Group.
Reach Group adheres in its operations and services provision to high level of quality and professional standards relying on extensive experiences and excellent networks in accordance with international best practices. Reach Group employs around 200 high caliber staff of different qualifications (Ph.D., M.Sc. & B.Sc.) and competencies (administration, finance, engineering, IT and others).
